Package: apt-auto-update
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, apt, cron | cron-daemon | systemd-cron, logrotate, sudo
Description: schedulable APT maintenance (Debian, Ubuntu, WSL, Raspberry Pi OS, …)
 Installs the apt-auto-update command: immediate run, enable or disable a daily
 cron job, and log rotation. Suitable for any APT-based system without relying
 on a user home directory.
